<br />
<br />I agree mostly with this. The context will usually make it clear.
<br />
<br />"I played TOP on an emulator"
<br />"I played TOP on my SNES"
<br />"I played TOP on my SNES using a flashcart"
<br />
<br />If you're playing on hardware, unless your flash/eprom cartridge doesn't work right, there's no difference between that and the official cartridge.

		

